## 0. Purpose

Defines the functions, permissions, and constraints governing the Sovereignty Lock. This API ensures that all PantheonOS modules operate under a single coherent operator identity with zero ambiguity.

---

## 1. Core Data Structures

```yaml
sovereignty_lock:
  state: locked | unlocked
  ethics_threshold: 0.7
  identity_anchor: apex
  temporal_sync: true
  activation_method:
    voice_seal: blake3_hash
    cadence: "4-2-6"
    perspective: "first-person"
